-- Edward Koch Discusses Life, Career in February 2011 (Audio)
-- B y
-- 2013-02-01T14:52:59Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-02-01/edward-koch-discusses-life-career-in-february-2011-audio-.html
Former  New York  City Mayor Edward I. 
Koch, who died today at age 88, had been the host of "Ed Koch - 
The Voice of Reason" and co-host of "A Touch of Clash" on 
Bloomberg Radio. In February 2011, he talked with Bloomberg 
Radio reporter Charlie Pellett about his life. The interview was
not aired until today.   (Source: Bloomberg)  Running time 27:47
 